
                       RubyWin

	July. 7, 2001  M.Suketa <CQN02273@nifty.ne.jp>

[What is RubyWin ?]
RubyWin is an IDE for Ruby on Windows. Using RubyWin, You can
learn about Ruby more easily. :-)
RubyWin works on Windows 2000. (Maybe 95, 98, NT)
Feel free to email comments and bug reports to masaki.suketa@nifty.ne.jp.

[Remark]
This version is alpha version and buggy!!!

[Development Environment]
  Windows 2000
  Mingw32-GCC 2.95.2 (MSVCRT version)
  Ruby 1.6.4 [i386-mingw32]
  Scintilla 1.38

