[What is Ruby ?]
Ruby is an object-oriented script language, copyrighted free software 
by Yukihiro Matsumoto.

You can download src file of Ruby from

  ftp://ftp.ruby-lang.org/pub/ruby/

or Ruby official site:

   http://www.ruby-lang.org/


